  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Xenophon/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1134015-21.jpg" class="pil" alt="Xenophon" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Xenophon/">Xenophon</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          5月29日          想读      </div>

      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:亚里士多德 伦理学 政治哲...</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wqk2003/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3356741-2.jpg" class="pil" alt="北京小饼干" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wqk2003/">北京小饼干</a><br/>
